      "endSec": 4.937,
      "kind": "selling",
      "clip": "pt_feihuiguo/s1.mp4",
      "feature": "people",
      "hl": []
    },
    {
      "text": "跑义乌、广州的批发市场,听着风光,实际多累自己知道。",
      "startSec": 5.057,
      "endSec": 9.707,
      "kind": "selling",
      "clip": "pt_feihuiguo/s2.mp4",
      "feature": "loading",
      "hl": []
    },
    {
      "text": "来回机票、住一礼拜酒店,白天泡市场一件件挑,晚上还得对账打包。",
      "startSec": 9.827,
      "endSec": 14.983,
      "kind": "selling",
      "clip": "pt_feihuiguo/s3.mp4",
      "feature": "aisle",
      "hl": []
    },
    {
      "text": "更别说一趟得备齐大半年的货,资金一次压一大笔,选错还砸手里。",
      "startSec": 15.103,
      "endSec": 20.756,
      "kind": "selling",
      "clip": "pt_feihuiguo/s4.mp4",
      "feature": "wall",
      "hl": []
    },
    {
      "text": "人折腾一圈,钱没省多少,店里还得找人盯。",
      "startSec": 20.876,
      "endSec": 24.69,
      "kind": "selling",
      "clip": "pt_feihuiguo/s5.mp4",
      "feature": "people",
      "hl": []
    },
    {
      "text": "其实现在,这趟可以不用飞了。",
      "startSec": 24.81,
      "endSec": 27.5,
      "kind": "selling",
      "clip": "pt_feihuiguo/s6.mp4",
      "feature": "drone",
      "hl": []
